author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Shower tile plumbing tips…the secret to good cuts is patience. I cut the tile to match my pattern. Then I transfer the nipple location based on my spacers. Adding water to the carbide hole saw reduces tile chipping. I want this to be as accurate, clean, and neat as possible. If you’re tiling a shower check out our Video Library at homerepairtutor.com 👍🏽🔥#tile #showertile #bathroominspiration #goforit
